    ns4:appear-02.viewer <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#site_1> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#clothe_1> a <https://w3id.org/framester/data/propbank-3.4.0/RoleSet/clothe-01> ;
