    ns1:associatedWith <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Recover-02> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#personnel_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#EmergencyPersonnel> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#rescue_1> a <https://w3id.org/framester/data/propbank-3.4.0/RoleSet/rescue-01> .

