<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#scene_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Scene> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#several_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Several> .

