    ns4:wear-01.wearer <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#person_3> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#winter_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Winter> .

